{
  "url": "https://www.gptechadvisors.com/about/",
  "content": [
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "We value your privacy",
      "fontSize": "18px",
      "fontWeight": "700",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": ".cky-title"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience, serve personalised ads or content, and analyse our traffic. By clicking \"Accept All\", you consent to our use of cookies.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "We use cookies to help you navigate efficiently and perform certain functions. You will find detailed information about all cookies under each consent category below.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "The cookies that are categorised as \"Necessary\" are stored on your browser as they are essential for enabling the basic functionalities of the site. ... Show more",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Necessary cookies are required to enable the basic features of this site, such as providing secure log-in or adjusting your consent preferences. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable data.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Functional cookies help perform certain functionalities like sharing the content of the website on social media platforms, collecting feedback, and other third-party features.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Analytical cookies are used to understand how visitors interact with the website. These cookies help provide information on metrics such as the number of visitors, bounce rate, traffic source, etc.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Performance cookies are used to understand and analyse the key performance indexes of the website which helps in delivering a better user experience for the visitors.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Advertisement cookies are used to provide visitors with customised advertisements based on the pages you visited previously and to analyse the effectiveness of the ad campaigns.",
      "fontSize": "14px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(33, 33, 33)",
      "dataId": null,
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "STRUCTURE, STRENGTHEN, STREAMLINE,  SCALE",
      "fontSize": "18px",
      "fontWeight": "600",
      "color": "rgb(164, 227, 34)",
      "dataId": "cfe7e5",
      "selector": ".elementor-heading-title"
    },
    {
      "tag": "h1",
      "text": "About Us",
      "fontSize": "95px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
      "dataId": "31000285",
      "selector": ".elementor-heading-title"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Navigating the cybersecurity and compliance landscape can be very confusing and overwhelming without the right experience and guidance. At GrowthPoint, we use our experience to help our clients structure and strengthen their cybersecurity and compliance programs so that they can scale their business.",
      "fontSize": "18px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
      "dataId": "7026cbaf",
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
      "tag": "h2",
      "text": "Our Mission",
      "fontSize": "60px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(8, 15, 31)",
      "dataId": "a2692e5",
      "selector": ".elementor-heading-title"
    },
    {
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "GrowthPoint was created by founders who have scaled companies and have a strong desire to help other companies structure, strengthen, streamline, and scale their companies for success.  We leverage our decades of experience to help you – whether you are just starting out and need some free advice or starting to mature and scale and need more help, we can provide it.  We help companies in the regul",
      "fontSize": "18px",
      "fontWeight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(8, 15, 31)",
      "dataId": "8513ee0",
      "selector": "p"
    },
    {
